<qti-assessment-item xmlns="http://www.imsglobal.org/xsd/imsqtiasi_v3p0" xmlns:m="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML" xmlns:xsi="http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema-instance" identifier="Q40_v2" title="Q40_v2" time-dependent="false" adaptive="false" xsi:schemaLocation="http://www.imsglobal.org/xsd/imsqtiasi_v3p0 https://purl.imsglobal.org/spec/qti/v3p0/schema/xsd/imsqti_asiv3p0_v1p0.xsd">
  <qti-response-declaration identifier="RESPONSE" cardinality="single" base-type="identifier">
    <qti-correct-response>
      <qti-value>ChoiceC</qti-value>
    </qti-correct-response>
  </qti-response-declaration>
  <qti-outcome-declaration identifier="FEEDBACK" cardinality="single" base-type="identifier"/>
  <qti-outcome-declaration identifier="SOLUTION" cardinality="single" base-type="identifier"/>
  <qti-outcome-declaration identifier="SCORE" cardinality="single" base-type="float">
    <qti-default-value>
      <qti-value>0</qti-value>
    </qti-default-value>
  </qti-outcome-declaration>
  <qti-item-body>
    <p>Dos taxis cobran en función de la distancia <m:math><m:mi>d</m:mi></m:math> (en kilómetros) que recorre un pasajero.</p>
    <p>Para calcular el cobro total, en pesos, se utilizan las siguientes funciones:</p>
    <p>Taxi 1: <m:math><m:msub><m:mi>C</m:mi><m:mn>1</m:mn></m:msub><m:mo>(</m:mo><m:mi>d</m:mi><m:mo>)</m:mo><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>1200</m:mn><m:mo>+</m:mo><m:mn>300</m:mn><m:mi>d</m:mi></m:math></p>
    <p>Taxi 2: <m:math><m:msub><m:mi>C</m:mi><m:mn>2</m:mn></m:msub><m:mo>(</m:mo><m:mi>d</m:mi><m:mo>)</m:mo><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>2200</m:mn><m:mo>+</m:mo><m:mn>200</m:mn><m:mi>d</m:mi></m:math>. Se sabe que existe una distancia para la cual ambos taxis cobran el mismo monto. ¿Para cuántos kilómetros de recorrido ambos taxis cobran lo mismo?</p>
    <qti-choice-interaction response-identifier="RESPONSE" shuffle="false" max-choices="1">
      <qti-simple-choice identifier="ChoiceA">5<qti-feedback-inline identifier="FB_ChoiceA" outcome-identifier="FEEDBACK">Incorrecto. Si <m:math><m:mi>d</m:mi><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>5</m:mn></m:math>, entonces Taxi 1 cobra <m:math><m:mn>1200</m:mn><m:mo>+</m:mo><m:mn>300</m:mn><m:mo>×</m:mo><m:mn>5</m:mn><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>1200</m:mn><m:mo>+</m:mo><m:mn>1500</m:mn><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>2700</m:mn></m:math> y Taxi 2 cobra <m:math><m:mn>2200</m:mn><m:mo>+</m:mo><m:mn>200</m:mn><m:mo>×</m:mo><m:mn>5</m:mn><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>2200</m:mn><m:mo>+</m:mo><m:mn>1000</m:mn><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>3200</m:mn></m:math>. Como <m:math><m:mn>2700</m:mn><m:mo>≠</m:mo><m:mn>3200</m:mn></m:math>, ambos taxis no cobran lo mismo para 5 km.</qti-feedback-inline></qti-simple-choice>
      <qti-simple-choice identifier="ChoiceB">8<qti-feedback-inline identifier="FB_ChoiceB" outcome-identifier="FEEDBACK">Incorrecto. Si <m:math><m:mi>d</m:mi><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>8</m:mn></m:math>, entonces Taxi 1 cobra <m:math><m:mn>1200</m:mn><m:mo>+</m:mo><m:mn>300</m:mn><m:mo>×</m:mo><m:mn>8</m:mn><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>1200</m:mn><m:mo>+</m:mo><m:mn>2400</m:mn><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>3600</m:mn></m:math> y Taxi 2 cobra <m:math><m:mn>2200</m:mn><m:mo>+</m:mo><m:mn>200</m:mn><m:mo>×</m:mo><m:mn>8</m:mn><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>2200</m:mn><m:mo>+</m:mo><m:mn>1600</m:mn><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>3800</m:mn></m:math>. Como <m:math><m:mn>3600</m:mn><m:mo>≠</m:mo><m:mn>3800</m:mn></m:math>, ambos taxis no cobran lo mismo para 8 km.</qti-feedback-inline></qti-simple-choice>
      <qti-simple-choice identifier="ChoiceC">10<qti-feedback-inline identifier="FB_ChoiceC" outcome-identifier="FEEDBACK">¡Correcto! Si <m:math><m:mi>d</m:mi><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>10</m:mn></m:math>, entonces Taxi 1 cobra <m:math><m:mn>1200</m:mn><m:mo>+</m:mo><m:mn>300</m:mn><m:mo>×</m:mo><m:mn>10</m:mn><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>1200</m:mn><m:mo>+</m:mo><m:mn>3000</m:mn><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>4200</m:mn></m:math> y Taxi 2 cobra <m:math><m:mn>2200</m:mn><m:mo>+</m:mo><m:mn>200</m:mn><m:mo>×</m:mo><m:mn>10</m:mn><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>2200</m:mn><m:mo>+</m:mo><m:mn>2000</m:mn><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>4200</m:mn></m:math>. Como ambos montos son <m:math><m:mn>4200</m:mn></m:math>, los dos taxis cobran lo mismo para 10 km.</qti-feedback-inline></qti-simple-choice>
      <qti-simple-choice identifier="ChoiceD">100<qti-feedback-inline identifier="FB_ChoiceD" outcome-identifier="FEEDBACK">Incorrecto. Si <m:math><m:mi>d</m:mi><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>100</m:mn></m:math>, entonces Taxi 1 cobra <m:math><m:mn>1200</m:mn><m:mo>+</m:mo><m:mn>300</m:mn><m:mo>×</m:mo><m:mn>100</m:mn><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>1200</m:mn><m:mo>+</m:mo><m:mn>30&#160;000</m:mn><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>31&#160;200</m:mn></m:math> y Taxi 2 cobra <m:math><m:mn>2200</m:mn><m:mo>+</m:mo><m:mn>200</m:mn><m:mo>×</m:mo><m:mn>100</m:mn><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>2200</m:mn><m:mo>+</m:mo><m:mn>20&#160;000</m:mn><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>22&#160;200</m:mn></m:math>. Como <m:math><m:mn>31&#160;200</m:mn><m:mo>≠</m:mo><m:mn>22&#160;200</m:mn></m:math>, ambos taxis no cobran lo mismo para 100 km.</qti-feedback-inline></qti-simple-choice>
    </qti-choice-interaction>
    <qti-feedback-block identifier="FB_Default" outcome-identifier="FEEDBACK" show-hide="show">
      <qti-content-body>
        <p>No se registró una alternativa válida. Selecciona una opción para revisar el feedback correspondiente.</p>
      </qti-content-body>
    </qti-feedback-block>
    <qti-feedback-block identifier="show" outcome-identifier="SOLUTION" show-hide="show">
      <qti-content-body>
        <p><strong>Resolución paso a paso</strong></p>
        <ol>
          <li>
            <p><strong>Paso 1: Igualar los cobros de ambos taxis</strong></p>
            <p>Como se busca la distancia para la cual ambos cobran lo mismo, se igualan las funciones:</p>
            <p><m:math><m:msub><m:mi>C</m:mi><m:mn>1</m:mn></m:msub><m:mo>(</m:mo><m:mi>d</m:mi><m:mo>)</m:mo><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:msub><m:mi>C</m:mi><m:mn>2</m:mn></m:msub><m:mo>(</m:mo><m:mi>d</m:mi><m:mo>)</m:mo></m:math></p>
            <p>Entonces:</p>
            <p><m:math><m:mn>1200</m:mn><m:mo>+</m:mo><m:mn>300</m:mn><m:mi>d</m:mi><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>2200</m:mn><m:mo>+</m:mo><m:mn>200</m:mn><m:mi>d</m:mi></m:math></p>
          </li>
          <li>
            <p><strong>Paso 2: Reunir los términos con <m:math><m:mi>d</m:mi></m:math> en un lado y los números en el otro</strong></p>
            <p>Restamos <m:math><m:mn>200</m:mn><m:mi>d</m:mi></m:math> en ambos lados:</p>
            <p><m:math><m:mn>1200</m:mn><m:mo>+</m:mo><m:mn>100</m:mn><m:mi>d</m:mi><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>2200</m:mn></m:math></p>
            <p>Luego restamos <m:math><m:mn>1200</m:mn></m:math> en ambos lados:</p>
            <p><m:math><m:mn>100</m:mn><m:mi>d</m:mi><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>1000</m:mn></m:math></p>
          </li>
          <li>
            <p><strong>Paso 3: Despejar la distancia</strong></p>
            <p>Dividimos ambos lados por <m:math><m:mn>100</m:mn></m:math>:</p>
            <p><m:math><m:mi>d</m:mi><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mfrac><m:mn>1000</m:mn><m:mn>100</m:mn></m:mfrac><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>10</m:mn></m:math></p>
          </li>
          <li>
            <p><strong>Paso 4: Verificar el resultado en ambas funciones</strong></p>
            <p>Para Taxi 1:</p>
            <p><m:math><m:mn>1200</m:mn><m:mo>+</m:mo><m:mn>300</m:mn><m:mo>×</m:mo><m:mn>10</m:mn><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>1200</m:mn><m:mo>+</m:mo><m:mn>3000</m:mn><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>4200</m:mn></m:math></p>
            <p>Para Taxi 2:</p>
            <p><m:math><m:mn>2200</m:mn><m:mo>+</m:mo><m:mn>200</m:mn><m:mo>×</m:mo><m:mn>10</m:mn><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>2200</m:mn><m:mo>+</m:mo><m:mn>2000</m:mn><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>4200</m:mn></m:math></p>
            <p>Ambos resultados son iguales.</p>
          </li>
          <li>
            <p><strong>Conclusión</strong></p>
            <p>Los dos taxis cobran lo mismo cuando el recorrido es de 10 kilómetros.</p>
          </li>
        </ol>
      </qti-content-body>
    </qti-feedback-block>
  </qti-item-body>
  <qti-response-processing>
    <qti-response-condition>
      <qti-response-if>
        <qti-match>
          <qti-variable identifier="RESPONSE"/>
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">ChoiceC</qti-base-value>
        </qti-match>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="SCORE">
          <qti-base-value base-type="float">1</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="FEEDBACK">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">FB_ChoiceC</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="SOLUTION">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">show</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
      </qti-response-if>
      <qti-response-else-if>
        <qti-match>
          <qti-variable identifier="RESPONSE"/>
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">ChoiceA</qti-base-value>
        </qti-match>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="FEEDBACK">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">FB_ChoiceA</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="SOLUTION">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">show</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
      </qti-response-else-if>
      <qti-response-else-if>
        <qti-match>
          <qti-variable identifier="RESPONSE"/>
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">ChoiceB</qti-base-value>
        </qti-match>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="FEEDBACK">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">FB_ChoiceB</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="SOLUTION">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">show</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
      </qti-response-else-if>
      <qti-response-else-if>
        <qti-match>
          <qti-variable identifier="RESPONSE"/>
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">ChoiceD</qti-base-value>
        </qti-match>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="FEEDBACK">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">FB_ChoiceD</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="SOLUTION">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">show</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
      </qti-response-else-if>
      <qti-response-else>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="FEEDBACK">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">FB_Default</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="SOLUTION">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">show</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
      </qti-response-else>
    </qti-response-condition>
  </qti-response-processing>
</qti-assessment-item>